### resolve typed identifiers -> stable node IDs
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/graph/resolve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": ["123", "456"],
  "phoneNos": ["+79995556677"],
  "partyRks": ["7700000000"]
}

### one-hop expansion from stable IDs
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/graph/one-hop
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seeds": ["person:123", "company:7700000000"],
  "cursor": "",
  "limit": 50,
  "edgeKinds": ["transfer", "contact"]
}

### one-hop expansion by typed identifiers (aliases supported)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/graph/one-hop
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": ["123"],
  "phone_no": ["+79995556677"],
  "party_rk": ["7700000000"],
  "limit": 50
}

### shortest path between stable IDs
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/graph/shortest-path
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "person:123",
  "to": "phone:+79995556677",
  "edgeKinds": ["transfer", "contact"],
  "maxHops": 6
}
